### Root URL
GET http://{{ENDPOINT}}

?? status == 200


### System info
GET http://{{ENDPOINT}}/info

?? status == 200
?? body uptime isString
?? body cpuCount isNumber


### Request inspection GET
GET http://{{ENDPOINT}}/inspect

?? status == 200
?? body remoteAddr isString
?? body method == GET


### Request inspection POST
POST http://{{ENDPOINT}}/inspect
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dave",
  "age": 42
}

?? status == 200
?? body body includes Dave
?? body method == POST


### System health
GET http://{{ENDPOINT}}/health

?? status == 200
?? body includes OK


### Random numbers
GET http://{{ENDPOINT}}/number/5000

?? status == 200
?? body matches ^\d+


### Random words
GET http://{{ENDPOINT}}/word/4

?? status == 200
?? body matches ^\D+


### Status code
GET http://{{ENDPOINT}}/status/418

?? status == 418